visual.name: Advanced Toggle Switch by TME AG
visual.displayName: Advanced Toggle Switch by TME AG
visual.description: Show and hide multiple data fields with switch on/off

licenseKey.description: License key to activate all pro features

filteType.description: Set a filter for ON and OFF field values

turnOnValue.description: Set comma seperated values from data field to filter data when switch is turned on

turnOffValue.description: Leave it blank if all values should be visible when switch is turned off

onColor.description: Sets bg color of switch, when turned on

offColor.description: Sets bg color of switch, when turned off

unselectedColor.description: Sets bg color of switch, when it's in unselected state

manageSize.description: Turn on to set the size of toggle to manage width and height individually

size.description: Manage height, width of actual toggle switch

onTitle.description: Set title for switch on state

offTitle.description: Set title for switch off state

unselectedTitle.description: Set title for unseleted switch state
